text: The canton of Dieppe-1 is an administrative division of the Seine-Maritime department, in northern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Dieppe.Décret n° 2014-266 du 27 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département de la Seine-Maritime It consists of the following communes: #Ambrumesnil #Aubermesnil-Beaumais #Colmesnil-Manneville #Dieppe (partly) #Hautot-sur-Mer #Longueil #Martigny #Offranville #Ouville-la-Rivière #Quiberville #Rouxmesnil-Bouteilles #Saint-Aubin-sur-Scie #Saint-Denis-d'Aclon #Sainte-Marguerite-sur-Mer #Sauqueville #Tourville-sur-Arques #Varengeville- sur-Mer ==References== Category:Cantons of Seine-Maritime Category:Dieppe
